snippet.textDisplay: For those that haven't read the Manhwa, after reading it all, I finally realized why the series is so familiar.  Other than the character Rachel, the entire series is almost a 1 to 1 copy of Hunter x Hunter.  From the characters to their backgrounds.  So much is similar.  NOT that that is a bad thing.  HxH is amazing and this emulates it so well (almost to close), but different enough that it's still enjoyable.
snippet.textOriginal: For those that haven't read the Manhwa, after reading it all, I finally realized why the series is so familiar.  Other than the character Rachel, the entire series is almost a 1 to 1 copy of Hunter x Hunter.  From the characters to their backgrounds.  So much is similar.  NOT that that is a bad thing.  HxH is amazing and this emulates it so well (almost to close), but different enough that it's still enjoyable.
